source.name: Antitrust Division Select Case Filings
source.description: Index of select cases and documents filed by the U.S. Department of Justice, Antitrust Division since January 1993. Cases are listed alphabetically by the last name of individual defendants, by company name, or by the entity's first name. Amicus curiae briefs are listed by plaintiff name.
